title: Billy Joel - Storm Front 320cbr 1989 Original CDRip
description:
Source: 1989 CD

Billy Joel - Storm Front 320cbr (Big Papi) 1989 Original CD Rip "We Didn't Start The Fire"


By Michael Patrick Boyd
Storm Front by Billy Joel forty-four minutes thirty-four seconds and was released on October 31, 1989. Storm Front reached #1 on the U.S. Billboard 200 Album charts for one week and went 4x Platinum. Six of the songs reached the billboard charts. We Didn't Start the Fire reached number one in four different categories. Okay this is not typical Billy Joel; this is more like an experimental cassette. Gone is most of his soft rock and easy listening and the piano is not included in all songs. Still this is a pretty good cassette. Storm Front by Billy Joel gets an AAA+++.
